#note a missed opportunity here, I had previously recognize the strength of the ABELR leave, but then neglected its potency on this play. I can play REW for 30 keeping ABLR, which is extremely powerful with a Y and two Es open for -ABLE/-ABLY bingos. after REW, I bingo 40% of the time, versus 12% after BRAWLER.
>Andrew_Fisher: BIO 14B BIO +22 297
